I"š<p>This CD is available now on the <a href="http://soundanatomy.com/">Sound Anatomy</a> label. I joined the core Lightning Ensemble trio of <a href="href=&quot;http://richard-scott.net/">Richard Scott</a>, Philip Marks and <a href="https://davidmbirchall.com/">David Birchall</a> on several tracks. Recorded by <a href="http://www.cuspeditions.co.uk/">Sam Weaver</a> on the 5th floor of <a href="http://www.islingtonmill.com/">Islington Mill</a>, Salford. What the trio have worked on together over many years is somehting really special, a shared improvising method that I very much enjoyed being a part of.</p>

